Should try to combine some CLI handler:
e.g. video show qam <id> psi
     video show qam <id> psi packet

Also some parameters checking may not be necessary, as they should be
done by the CLI parser.


The following two CLI gives about the same results:
  video show qam 0 program 1
  video show qam 0 program 1 psi

